   ,"title":"Polarization measurement of fast neutrons from the 9Be(alpha,n)12C and the 13C(alpha,n)16O reaction using a high-pressure 4He-polarimeter in a new design"
   ,"x4subents":[
   {"SUBENT":"F0699001", "isub":1, "compiled":20251222, "TransID":"F105", "TransDate":20260305
